---
---
<section id="ai" class="section ai">
  <div class="container ai-inner">
    <div class="ai-copy">
      <span class="eyebrow">AI commits, local-first</span>
      <h2>Your diff never has to leave your laptop.</h2>
      <p>
        Run <code>gitb commit ai</code> against a hosted provider — OpenAI or
        OpenRouter (Gemini, Claude, GPT, DeepSeek and more) — or pick
        <strong>Ollama</strong> to keep the entire flow on
        <code>localhost</code>. No key, no network, no third-party retention
        policy to read.
      </p>
      <ul class="ai-points">
        <li>
          <span class="ok">✓</span> Provider switch in a single menu — your
          team can choose its own privacy policy.
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="ok">✓</span> Keys resolved from env vars first
          (<code>GITB_AI_API_KEY_OPENAI</code>, …), then per-repo, then global.
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="ok">✓</span> Messages follow Conventional Commits — type,
          scope, subject, body — ready for changelog tooling.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="ai-demo">
      <div class="terminal">
        <div class="terminal-header">
          <span class="dot red"></span>
          <span class="dot yellow"></span>
          <span class="dot green"></span>
          <span class="title">setup — fully local</span>
        </div>
        <div class="terminal-body">
<pre><code><span class="dim"># one-time setup</span>
<span class="prompt-arrow">❯</span> brew install ollama
<span class="prompt-arrow">❯</span> ollama serve <span class="flag">&</span>
<span class="prompt-arrow">❯</span> ollama pull qwen3:8b
<span class="prompt-arrow">❯</span> gitb cfg ai
  <span class="info">Provider:</span>  <span class="tip">ollama</span>
  <span class="info">Model:</span>     <span class="tip">qwen3:8b</span>
  <span class="info">Endpoint:</span>  <span class="tip">http://localhost:11434</span>

<span class="dim"># forever after</span>
<span class="prompt-arrow">❯</span> gitb commit ai
  <span class="ok">✓</span> message generated locally in 1.4s
  <span class="ok">✓</span> nothing left this machine</code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .ai {
    background:
      linear-gradient(180deg, transparent, rgba(121, 192, 255, 0.04) 50%, transparent),
      transparent;
  }

  .ai-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(0, 1.05fr);
    gap: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .ai-copy h2 {
    margin-top: 0.8rem;
  }

  .ai-copy p {
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    max-width: 560px;
  }

  .ai-points {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 1rem 0 0;
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    color: var(--fg-muted);
  }

  .ai-points .ok {
    color: var(--green);
    margin-right: 0.4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .ai-demo pre {
    background: transparent;
    border: 0;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 880px) {
    .ai-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
